import React from 'react'
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';



export const DosageCats = () => {
  return (
    <>
    
    <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
      <option>How much food you need based on your cat weight ?</option>
      <option value="1">5kg = 100g</option>
      <option value="2">10kg = 200g</option>
      <option value="3">15kg = 300g</option>
      <option value="4">20kg = 400g</option>
    </Form.Select>

    <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
      <option>How much water you need based on your cat weight ?</option>
      <option value="1">5kg = 250ml</option>
      <option value="2">10kg = 500ml</option>
      <option value="3">15kg = 750ml</option>
      <option value="4">20kg = 1000ml</option>
    </Form.Select>
      
      </>
  )
}
